is pretty well known as being one of the most clever bards in EQ. Trust me, I got abused in enough faggot ways (charm burning with WW dragons, etc) to believe that he can figure out how to push the limits of EQ game design in about any way possible. He's been one of the first bards or the first to discover about any exploit that's been used in the last 18 months or so, and is certainly unabashed about using them till they are fixed.<br>
<br>
I wonder if anyone still has the screenshot of one of the SZ GM's broadcasting that he couldn't do anything about Worry charm burning all of OT with the General in the bank - literally shutting down the entire zone (you'd zone in, get summoned and raped - he did the same thing with WW dragons, trying to run to ToV was the gayest shit ever - they'd have 3 or 4 bards doing it). It wasn't against the rules though, more power to him.<br>
<br>
Anyways, he's been doing the HoH sploit for a while, was wondering how long it would last for. He's made a ton of cash (both $$ and pp) for charm burning and other exploits for droppable items and PL'ing ... payed for a pretty nice car among other things. I doubt he's to mad this got fixed, he'll find another one soon.<br>
<br>
The worst part of it is that Worry has always taken work other bards (Pino/Juniper/Xenora especially - another SZ/Legends bard and the best one in the game, hands down - he must be a concert pianist to play like he does) and made them 10x worse and then made GM's aware of them when he's tired of it. A lot of bards don't like him for that, and for his willingness to 'sell them out' when he's done with something. <p><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;font-family:courier;font-size:small;">&quot;It never stops hurting, you just go faster...&quot;</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--> - <!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:red;font-family:courier;font-size:small;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Greg LeMond</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=velaelsoulrender>Velael Soulrender</A> at: 4/25/03 11:11:52 am<br></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#ffffff>- </font><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation>Graffë's Wizard Discussion</a><font color=#ffffff> - </font><a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1>General EQ Discussion</a> <font color=#ffffff> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.240<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

